TEXT -952 1664 Left 2 !.measure tran iavg AVG i(V1) from=4u to=5u\n.measure tran iclk_phi2_avg AVG i(V6) from=4u to=5u\n.measure tran iclk_phi1_avg AVG i(V7) from=4u to=5u\n \n.measure tran pclk2 PARAM='-iclk_phi2_avg*3.3'\n.measure tran pclk1 PARAM='-iclk_phi1_avg*3.3'\n.measure tran pavg PARAM='-iavg*3.3'\n.measure tran ptot PARAM='pavg+pclk1+pclk2'
